window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Love, magic, faith. All roads lead to Camlann as Arthur gathers his men for a single battle - a final great contest against the full might of Modred and his Saxon army. Wales will win all or lose all in one last throw of the dice.</p> <p><i>Frost Against the Hilt </i>is the fifth and final installment in the Lion of Wales series.</p> <p><b>Complete Series listening order</b>:</p> <ol> <li><i>Cold My Heart</i></li> <li><i>The Oaken Door</i></li> <li><i>Of Men and Dragons</i></li> <li><i>A Long Cloud</i></li> <li><i>Frost Against the Hilt</i></li> </ol>"; 
